{
  "comment": "Registry of source-built apps. `kind` selects the build tool: `koto` uses the koto-compiler (high-level source), `asm` uses kbc-asm (low-level IR). `output` is the committed bytecode under sdcard_mock; `manifest` must declare it as the entry. An optional `maps` block embeds `*.txt` tilemaps from `dir` into `source` (between the generated-stage markers) at build time. An optional `images` block compiles `.kspr` ASCII sprite sheets into committed `.kim` (KIM1 RGB565) package assets. Rebuild with `python harness/build_apps.py`; verify drift with `--check`.",
